{"sectionId":490,"sectionIdLiteral":"490","humanId":"lesson-86","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"ownlineNumber":"Lesson 86"},"annotation":"W-86","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text review-lesson review-2 lesson-86\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"490#0\"><p class=\"p-review-intro\"><span data-sentence-id=\"490#0:1\">These ideas are for review today:</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"490#1\"><p class=\"p-lesson-ref\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>(<span class=\"lref\">71</span>) <b>Only God‚Äôs plan for salvation will work.</b></span></p> <p class=\"p-normal\"><span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>It is senseless for me to search wildly about for salvation.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>I have seen it in many people and in many things, but when I reached for it, it was not there.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>I was mistaken about where it is.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>I was mistaken about what it is.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>I will undertake no more idle seeking.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>Only God‚Äôs plan for salvation will work.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#1:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>And I will rejoice because His plan can never fail.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"490#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>These are some suggested forms for applying this idea specifically:</span></p> <p class=\"p-prayer\"><span data-sentence-id=\"490#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>God‚Äôs plan for salvation will save me from my perception of this.<br/></span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>This is no exception in God‚Äôs plan for my salvation.<br/></span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Let me perceive this only in the light of God‚Äôs plan for salvation.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"490#3\"><p class=\"p-lesson-ref\"><span class=\"pnr\">3.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#3:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>(<span class=\"lref\">72</span>) <b>Holding grievances is an attack on God‚Äôs plan for salvation.</b></span></p> <p class=\"p-normal\"><span data-sentence-id=\"490#3:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Holding grievances is an attempt to prove that God‚Äôs plan for salvation will not work.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#3:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Yet only His plan will work.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#3:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>By holding grievances, I am therefore excluding my only hope of salvation from my awareness.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#3:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>I would no longer defeat my own best interests in this insane way.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#3:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>I would accept God‚Äôs plan for salvation, and be happy.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"490#4\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">4.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#4:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Specific applications for this idea might be in these forms:</span></p> <p class=\"p-prayer\"><span data-sentence-id=\"490#4:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>I am choosing between misperception and salvation as I look on this.<br/></span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#4:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>If I see grounds for grievances in this, I will not see the grounds for my salvation.<br/></span> <span data-sentence-id=\"490#4:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>This calls for salvation, not attack.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"These ideas are for review today: (71) Only God‚Äôs plan for salvation will work. It is senseless for me to search wildly